    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Pepperfry",
    "description": "Join the Pepperfry family as a SEO Specialist in Chennai. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Pepperfry:\nPepperfry is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pepperfry!",
